org.yawlfoundation.yawl.worklet.exception

Class ExletRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.yawlfoundation.yawl.worklet.selection.AbstractRunner
      • org.yawlfoundation.yawl.worklet.exception.ExletRunner

  • public class ExletRunner
extends AbstractRunner
    The ExletRunner class manages an exception handling process. An instance of this class is created for each exception process raised by a case. This class also manages running worklet instances for a 'parent' case when required. The key data member is the RdrConclusion _conclusion, which contains the sequential set of exception handling primitives for this particular handler.
    Version:
    0.8, 04-09/2006; updated for v4 9/2015
    Author:
    Michael Adams
